				and icons from
				<a href="https://icons8.com/">icons8</a>.
				<br>
				<br>
				Team roles:
				<br>
				<br>
				API handling for weather and cities: Toni
				<br>
				<br>
				Search function for the locations: Quan
				<br>
				<br>
				Layout design and travel initiary form and database: Hetti
			</p>
		</div>
	</main>
	{% include 'footer.html' %}
{% endblock %}
